mixin Tricks()
    section.tricks.container
        h2 How to Create the Perfect Organized Space
        p Here are some expert tips on how to organize your storage efficiently:
        ul.tricks__list
            li.tricks__item Use bins and containers – keep items dust-free and neatly stored.
            li.tricks__item Group items by category – separate documents from clothing, for example.
            li.tricks__item Try vacuum storage bags – instantly free up closet space.
            li.tricks__item Label your containers – find things faster with clear labels.
            li.tricks__item With the right approach, even a small apartment can feel spacious and clutter-free!